rows.label: bf11430150_0020
rows.name: You're very capable, even on your own.

rows.label: bf11430150_0030
rows.name: Ah, well maybe I should thank him... Or not.

rows.label: bf11430150_0070
rows.name:
A being with human and Blade cells,
made possible with Judician technology.

rows.label: bf11430150_0080
rows.name:
That's how I can use my full strength
anywhere, without my Driver.

rows.label: bf11430150_0085
rows.name:
But I'm pretty sure I'm a failed
experiment, so to speak.

rows.label: bf11430150_0090
rows.name: I never knew Blades like that existed.

rows.label: bf11430150_0110
rows.name:
What of Marveni?
Isn't he coming?

rows.label: bf11430150_0120
rows.name:
Nah.. I just heard rumors that you guys
had entered Iira.

rows.label: bf11430150_0150
rows.name: It's been two years since I saw him last.
